high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the toilet.
Pick up the bottle off of the toilet tank.
Turn left and walk over to the metal shelving unit.
Put the bottle on the top shelf of the metal shelving unit.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the bottle off of the counter.
Walk back over to the metal shelving unit.
Put the bottle next to the other bottle on the top shelf of the metal shelving unit.
anns.task_desc: Move two bottles to a metal shelving unit.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward to the toilet paper holder to the left of the toilet.
Take the bottle from the top of the toilet tank.
Turn left, go forward to the metal rack.
Put the bottle on the top metal rack to the left of the yellow spray bottle.
Turn around, go forward to the toilet, turn right, go forward to the vanity.
Take the bottle from the right side of the vanity.
Turn around, go forward to the toilet paper holder, turn left, go forward to the metal rack.
Put the bottle on the top metal rack to the left of the first bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put two bottles on a metal rack.
